
'''= a site built and run by open innovation participants for all open innovation solvers'''

URL = http://openoi.com/



=Description=

"This is a platform that allows solvers, seekers and thinkers worldwide to share 
and work together on ideas, creative efforts, solutions, research and problems 
to be solved - anything when you get right down to it. These posted papers 
are then searchable not only on this site, but by search engines as well. And 
while this site is a natural companion to other OI platforms like Innocentive, 
nineSigma and IdealConnection to name a few, it is certainly not limited to 
such applications and other uses are always encouraged."


